    </edge>
    <data key="d0">Food Hub, Freightways, and Vertex Pharmaceuticals Architectures</data>
    <data key="d1">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=m4HbkhRw4UE</data>
    <data key="d2">This architecture combines three distinct customer use cases presented in the video. Food Hub handles high-scale order processing and real-time dashboarding for 28,000+ restaurants, particularly during weekend peak times. Freightways built a serverless tracking solution handling 1500 scans/minute, evolving from Amazon MQ to SNS/SQS for fan-out. Vertex Pharmaceuticals developed an intelligent serverless molecule search platform, dynamically creating compute environments for chemists to evaluate billions of molecules.</data>
    <data key="d3">data_ingestion, interactive, compute_intensive, control</data>
    <data key="d4">True</data>
  </graph>
</graphml>
